text.tspan: A rule has a before and an after side.
Shapes inside before and after have to be
same but can be of different colors.
Topological matches of the before side are
Step: Applies one rule one time
Run: Applies rules until stable each frame.
Slowmo: Applies one rule per frame.
Sleeping: Reset to normal each frame
Solid: matched rigidly, meaning the shape must match exactly
